item.title: Hockey Womens 1’s win again
item.author: Bryony Halcrow,
item.description: For the first match this year it was definitely thermal weather as the Ladies’ 1s went out to play RUMS in the arctic conditions found at Harlington, on a pitch that was nearly frozen, although this didn’t put a damper on our spirits. We were out to get them, as earlier in theseason they had beaten …
